        <num>CC 1511</num>
        <heading>1511.  Onerous donation, extent of reduction</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1511.  Onerous donation, extent of reduction
The value of an onerous donation is not included in the calculation of the forced portion, and the donation may not be reduced, unless the value of the charges is less than two-thirds the value of the property donated at the time of the donation, in which event the gratuitous portion is included in the calculation and is subject to reduction.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
